npm install express express-graphql graphql
npm i --save-dev nodemon


Run - if use postman, the following is how to post the request JSON
{ "query": "{ hello }" }

Example with easy data
https://www.fullstacklabs.co/blog/express-graphql-server

The hello-world.js implemented the basic Example
The index.js implemented some more realistic examples on query and mutations.

To run the example
npm start
and go to localhost:4000/graphql in the browser